    <h2>Summary of Key Equations</h2>
    <div class="equations">
      1. τ = r·F·sin(θ) &nbsp;&nbsp;(Torque)<br>
      2. I = (2/5)·m·r² &nbsp;&nbsp;(Moment of Inertia for Sphere)<br>
      3. τ = I·α &nbsp;&nbsp;(Torque Equation)<br>
      4. v = ω·r &nbsp;&nbsp;(Linear-Angular Relationship)
    </div>

